quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,"Senaare wondani oon do∆īnu…óo Jeyaa…óo makko on jehma, iwde ta juulirde hormante haa ka juulirde wo…ó…óitiinde, nden nde min mbarkini banŇče mun,fii yo min kollu mo immorde e aayeeje amen. Pellet, Ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ji‚Äôoowo."
  17,2,"Min njnniino Muusaa deftere nden, men mba…ói nde peewal, wonan'de …ďi…ó…ďe Israa‚Äôiila …ďen, won'de : ""Wata on njogito ga Am kooloraa…óo""."
  17,3,"[Ko onon yo] …ďi…ó…ďe …ďe …ďe min mba…ó…óinnoo wonnudude e Nuuhu.Pellet, o laatino jeyaa…óo yettoowo."
  17,4,"Min mbahyinino e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa‚Äôiila …ďe to deftere [won'de] : ""On mbonnayat ta leydi laabi …ói…ói, on townitoyto kadi townitaare mawnnde""."
  17,5,"Si fodoore gootel e …óin …ói…ói arii, min ngurta e mon jiyaa…ďe Amen, mar…ďe doole tii…ó…óe, …ďe njiloo hakkunde galleeji …ói. ∆äuum wonii fodoore huuwoyteende =golloteende."
  17,6,"Refti min nduttitanani on n on doole …óen e hoore ma…ď…ďe; min ∆Āeydi on jaw…óe e …ďi…ó…ďe,min mba…óa on gorol …ďurngol heewde."
  17,7,"Si on mo∆ī∆īinii, ko ko'e mon mo∆ī∆īinan…óon ; si on mbonnii kadi, ko ko‚Äôe mon [bonnann…óon]. Si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, ko fii yo …ďe hoynu j'eece mon …óen, e fii yo no …ďe naatiraa ka juulirde wano …ďe naatirnoo e mayre ka laawol adanol, e fii yo …ďe muncu yeru woo ko …ďe townani muncudee."
  17,8,"Hino jortaa ka Joomi mon yurmee on.Si on fillitike (non),min fillitoo. min mba…óanii yeddu…ďe …ďe Jahannama on tonngorde."
  17,9,"Pellet, ndee Alqur‚Äôaanaare no fewnat e ko …ďuri e nuun…óude,hende wewlinira=weltanira gooŇč…óin…ďe,…ďen golloo…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin, won'de, no woodani …ďe njo…ďdi mawndi."
  17,10,"E won'de pellet, …ďen …ďe gooŇč…óinaa laakara on, men maranii …ďe lepte muusu…óe."
  17,11,"Ne…ó…óo no toroo bone, wano o tororta non mo∆ī∆īere,ne…ó…óaŇčke on wonii ko he√Īii…óo."
  17,12,"Min mba…óii jemma on e √Īalawma on Aayeeje …ói…ói, min momti aaya jemma on, min mba…ói aaya √Īalawma on hentii…óo, fii yo on …óa…ď…ďu …ďural immorde e Joomi mon, e fii yo on ngandu limoore duu…ďi, e hasboore. Kala huunde, min n fensitirii nde fensitudee."
  17,13,"Kala ne…ó…óaŇčke, min mba…ó…óinii mo talkuru makko ndun ka daande makko. Men njaltinanoyat mo √Ďande Darngal, deftere, o hawra e mayre ko nde fontaande."
  17,14,"Janngu deftere maa nden, hoore-maa yonante hannde kasboowo."
  17,15,"Mo feewii, haray pellet, ko hoore-makko o feewani ; mo majii kadi, haray pellet, ko o majji kon yantate hoore-makko. WoŇčkii ronndotaako bone wokki goo. Men ngonaani leptoo…ďe, haa min immina Nulaa…óo."
  17,16,"Si min faandike halkude saare, Men y Njamirat neeminaa…ďe mayre …ďen, …ďe faasinqinoo e mayre, konngol (lepte) ngol jojja e mayre, Men munca nde muncudee."
  17,17,"Heewii gire …óe min kalki …ďaawo Nuuhu! Joomi maa Yonii Humpitii…óo, ji‚Äôoowo junuubi=bakkatuuji jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen."
  17,18,"Kala mo faala yaawnaneede, min n njaawnanat mo ton huunde ko min muuyi, wonan'de on mo min nj…ói, refti min mba…óana mo Jahannama, o naatoya nge ko o √ĪiŇčaa…óo, go…ó…óinaa…óo [yurmeende]."
  17,19,"On paalaa…óo laakara, o gollani …óum golle mum, hara kaŇčko ko o gooŇč…óin…óo ;…ďeen …óoon, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen ngonii jaarnaa…óe."
  17,20,"Kala (ma…ď…ďe),mi…óen …ďeydana ; …ďee …óoo e …ďee …óoo, immorde e dokkal Joomi maa. Dokkal Joomi maa ngal wonaani ka…óaa ngal."
  17,21,"Ndaarii no min …ďurniri yoga ma…ď…ďe e dow yoga, ko laakara on …ďuri mawnude darjaaji,…ďuri mawnude kadi …ďural."
  17,22,"Wota a wa…óan Alla dewetee…óo go…ó…óo; njoo…óoyo…óaa ko a √ĪiŇčaa…óo noppaa…óo."
  17,23,"Joomi maa yamirii :""wota on ndew ko wonaa KaŇčko, jipnaa…ďe …ď,mo∆ī∆īagol [e ma…ď…ďe]:si nayewu go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe yottike ma,maa …óum …ďe …ói…óo non;wota a wi‚Äôi …ďe ""eh=uf!"" wota a wikko …ďe =wota a furo,layan …ďe konngol teddungol."
  17,24,"Njankinano…óaa …ďe njurme…óaa …ďe, mbi‚Äôaa: ¬ę Joomi an, yurme …ďe‚Äôe, wano …ďe ne‚Äôirnoo kam non hari ko mi tosokum ¬Ľ."
  17,25,"Joomi mo'on no andi ko woni ka nder woŇčkiiji mon, si tawii on ngonnno mo∆ī∆īu…ďe ; pellet KaŇčko o wonanii ruttotoo…ďe …ďe cuhroowo."
  17,26,"Jonnu jom …ďadondiral haqqee makko o, e …ďillii…óo, e seteejo haqqee makko on ; wota a bonnu bonnere."
  17,27,"Pellet bonnoo…ďe …ďe, ko si…ó…ďe seytanuuji …ói ; seytaane non wonii jeddu…óo Joomi mum."
  17,28,"Si a …óuurniima …ďe fii …óa…ď…ďugol yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, nde jorti…óaa …óum, wi'i …ďe konngol newingol."
  17,29,"Wota a wa…ó junngo maa ngo ko lmbaango, ka daande maa ; wota a fortu ngo kadi kala portugol, haa njoo…óo…óaa ko a pelnii…óo, nimsu…óo."
  17,30,"Pellet Joomi maa, no yaacnana arsike, on mo O muuyi. O …ďittina. Pellet KaŇčko O wonii kumpitii…óo, ji‚Äôoowo jeyaa…ďe makko."
  17,31,"Wote on mbare …ďi…ď…ďe mon …ďen kulol …ďilla=ba'asal, ko minen ngarsikata …ďe, won'dude e mon ; pellet bargol …ďe ngol, wonii goopol manngol."
  17,32,"Wota on …ďatto jina=fijrde nde, pellet …óuum wonii paŇčkare e laawol bon'ngol."
  17,33,"Wota on mbar woŇčkii, ki Allah harmini kin [bargol], si wonaa sabu hakkee. Mo too√Īaama waraama, min wa…óanii heftu…ďe e makko …ďe doole wota non o fantin ka bargol. Pellet KaŇčko o wonii ballaa…óo."
  17,34,"Wota on …ďatto jawle Alyatiim, si wonaa …ďattagol …ďurngol mo∆ī∆īude, haa sagatalaaku makko timma ; kuumnee aadi ndin; pellet, aadi ndin wonii la…ďnditoytee ndi."
  17,35,"Kuu…ďnee …ďetu ngu si petat, manndikiron manndakke=peeson peese peew…óe, ko …óum mo∆ī∆īi, ko ka√Īum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude battane."
  17,36,"Wota a rewindo e ko a anndaa fii mum. Pellet nan…óe …óen, e gii…óe …óen e …ďernde nden, …óii…óoo fow ngonii la…ďnditoytee…ói ka makko."
  17,37,"Wota a yaaru e leydi √Īaa∆īa bunnga, ko fii pellet an a yulataa leydi ndin, a yottotaako pelle …óe njuuteendi."
  17,38,"…óe fof, bone majji on ngonii ga√Īaa…ói to Joomi maa."
  17,39,"∆äuum, ko go…ó…óum e ko Joomi maa…óa wahayini fa'ade e maa, immorde e √Ďee√Īal wota a wa…ó dewetee…óo goo wond'ude e Alla, sakko mberle…óaa ka ndeer jahannama ko a pelaa…óo da…óaa…óo."
  17,40,"E mati Joomi mon su…ďani on …ďi…ď…ďe wor…ďe, O jogitoo immorde e malaa'ikaaji …ói rew…ďe? Pellet, onon ho…óon layde konngol mawnungol!"
  17,41,"GooŇč…óii min fensitii e nder ndee Alqur'aanaare fii yo …ďe mbaactor, …óum …ďeydaani …ďe si wonaa wo…ó…óitagol."
  17,42,""" Maaku : ¬ę Si tawno no won'di e makko, dewetee…ói wano …ďe mbi‚Äôiri ni …ói …óa…ď…ďayno laawol feewde de Jom Arsi o."""
  17,43,"Senaade wonanii mo, o Toowii gaayi e ko …ďe mbi'ata Toowal mawnngal."
  17,44,"No subunhinan'de mo kammuuli …óin jee…ói…ói e leydi ndin e …ďe won'…ďe e majji, alaa e hay e hu'unde si wonaa hende Subunhinaade sabu Yettugol mo, kono on faamataa cubunhinaali ma…ď…ďe …óin, pellet, KaŇčko O wonii mun√Īii…óo cuhroowo."
  17,45,"Si a janngii Alqur'aanaare nden min ma…óat hakkunde maa e …ďeen …ďe mgooŇč…óinaa laalara on heedo suu…óiingo."
  17,46,"Min mba…ói a…ói e dow …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen cokoo…óe fii wata …ďe paamu nde [Alqur'aanaare nden] e ka noppi ma…ď…ďe kadi teddeele, si a jaŇčtike Joomi maa…óa ka ndeer Alqur'aanaare KaŇčko Tun …ďe huccinay …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko …ďe dogoo…ďe."
  17,47,"Ko Minen ngnndi ko …ďe ke…óotoo kon, tuma …ďe ke…óotoo fa'ade e maa…óa [yo Nulaa…óo], e tuma …ďe cowndondirta=ndeeydata, tuma nde too√Īoo…ďe …ďe mbi'ata: ¬ęOn jokkaani si wonaa gorko mbil…óaa…óo=bilaa…óo¬Ľ."
  17,48,"Ndaarii [yo Nulaa…óo] ko honno …ďe piyiranay maa mise=yeruuji, …ďe majjii …ďe kattantaake [he…ďde] laawol."
  17,49,"∆Āe mbi'i: ¬ęE hara si mon mgonii ∆īi'e e ngu…óu, haray ko min immintinoytee…ďe tagoore hesre?¬Ľ"
  17,50,"Maaku: [yo Nulaa…óo] ¬ęngonee kaa∆īe maa jam…óe¬Ľ"
  17,51,"Ma …óuum tagoore tawa nde mawni e …ďer…óe mon, …ďe mbi'a: 'Ko hommbo ruttata amen?"" Maaku: ""Ko On tak…óo on ka laawol adanol"". ∆Āe tura ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óe fa'ade e maa, …ďe mbi'a: ""∆äuum ko honde tuma""?, Maaku: 'No tijjaa nde tawata …ďadike""."
  17,52,"√Ďannde o noddata on nooto…óon njetton mo cikkon on √Īii…ďaano [ka leydi] si wonaa see…óa."
  17,53,"Maakan jiyaa…ďe aan …ďe: ""Yoo …ďe lay ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, pellet, Seytaane o bonnat hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, pellet, Seytaane wonanii ne…ó…óaŇčke ga√Īo laa…ďtu…óo""."
  17,54,"Joomi mon ko o ganndo fii mon, si o yi…óii o yurmoo on, maa …óum si o yi…óii olepta on. Min nulaani ma e dow ma…ď…ďe fawtii…óo."
  17,55,"Ko Joomi maa anndi fii …ďe won…ďe ta kammuuli e ta leydi, pellet, Min …ďurnii wo…ď…ďe e Annabaa…ďe …ďe e dow wo…ď…ďe, Min Jonni Daawuuda Jabuura."
  17,56,"Maaku: ""Noddee …ďe …ďe aa∆īi…óon [ko dewetee…ďe] gaanin makko, …ďe maraa huncugol lorra kan gaayi mo'on wonaa waylugol kadi""."
  17,57,"∆Āen, …ďe …ďe ngoni noddude, he…ďe …óa…ď…ďude …óoworgal fa'ade e Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri …ďadaade, he…ďe njoortii yurmende makko on he…ďe kuli lepte makko …óe, pellet, lepte Joomi maa …óe …óe laatike ko deentaa…óe."
  17,58,"Alaa e saare si wonaa minen ko min halkat…ďe nde ko adii √Īande darngal, maa ko min leptat…ďe nde lepte cattu…óe, …óuum …óo wonii ko winndaa …óum to Deftere."
  17,59,"Ha…óaani min nde min nula aayeeje …óe, si wona sabu yeddiino …óe adii…ďe …ďen, Min okki Samuuda Ngeelooba ba yi'teemba …ďe too√Īi ba, Min nuliraani Aayeeje …óe si wonaa hul…ďinir…óe."
  17,60,"[Janto] Tuma nde min wi'anno maa: ""Pellet, Joomi maa o hu…ďindima yim…ďe …ďe, Min mba…óiraani nde yi'annde nde Min kollumaa si wonaa fitina wona'de yim…ďe …ďe e lekki hu…óaaki ki ka Alqur'aana, Mi…óen kul…ďina …ďe kono …ďeydataa …ďe si wonaa bewre mawnde."
  17,61,"Nde min n Daalannoo Maleykaaji …ói cujjanee aadama, …ďe cujji si wonaa Ibliisa o wi'i: "" mi sujjanta on mo tal…óa e loopal?""."
  17,62,"O wi'i: ""A yi'ii oo mo teddin…óaa e dow am, pellet, si A nee…ďnanii kan haa √Īande darnga mi bonnat …ďi…ď…ďe makko …ďe si wonaa see…óaa…ďe."
  17,63,"[Alla] Daali: ""Yahu, kala jokku…óo ma e ma…ď…ďe pellet, ko jahannama woni njo…ďdi mon, njo…ďdi yonoori""."
  17,64,"Dillinir on mo kattana…óaa e ma…ď…ďe hito maa o, poo…óa e dow ma…ď…ďe pucci maa e seppoo…ďe maa, rentu e ma…ď…ďe jawle e …ďi…ď…ďe fodu…ďe, [kono] Seytaane fodaani …ďe si wonaa hodo."
  17,65,"Pellet, Jiyaa…ďe am …ďe a maraa doole e hoore ma…ď…ďe, Joomi maa yonii kooloraa…óo."
  17,66,"Ko Joomi mon woni sogganat…óo on laa…óe …óe e maayo, fii yo on …óa…ď…ďu immorde e …ďural makko , pellet, KaŇčko ko O jurmotoo…óo on."
  17,67,"Si lorra he…ďii on to maayo, majja …ďeen …ďe noddatno …óon, si wonaa KaŇčko [Alla] nde danndi on ka njorndi …óurno…óon, ne…ó…óaŇčke on wonii te o seeraani won'de heewu…óo jeddugol."
  17,68,"Enee, on kooli mutintaa on ka baŇče njorndi maa…óum o nula e mon damagariire [to…ďo koccu], refti he…ďantaake on fawtii…óo."
  17,69,"Ma kooli o nduttaraa on e maggo laawol goo o accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli o yoolira on sabu ko njedduno …óon ko, refti on ke…ďantaake jokkitirat…óo e dow amen cukkoowo."
  17,70,"GooŇč…óii, min teddinii …ďi…ó…ďe aadama …ďe, min ronndike …ďe ka njorndi e ka maayo min arsiki …ďe immorde e laa…ďu…ói min n …ďurni …ďe e dow ko heewi e …ďen …ďe min tagi …ďurnudee."
  17,71,"√Ďannde min noddiroyta kala yim…ďe gardii…óo ma…ď…ďe on,kala on jonnitiroyaa…óo deftere makko nde ka √Īaamo makko …ďe …óon …ďe janngay deftere ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe too√Īirtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro."
  17,72,"Kala on gon'…óo e [ngurndan aduna] ko o bun…óo, haray kaŇčko, ko ka laakara o …ďurata wumde e majjude laawol."
  17,73,"Fii kala …ďe e…ď…ďii nde …ďe fitinatmaa gaayi nde hu'unde nde min n wahayini e maa…óa fii yo a fekindo e amen ko wonaa …óun [ko min n tellini e maa] on tuma …ďe njogitoto ma sehlaajo."
  17,74,"Si tawiino min tabintinaanoma, gooŇč…óii a do'ii oo√Īa'ade e ma…ď…ďe hu'unde see…óaare."
  17,75,"On tuma min mee…óinteno cowale [lepte] ka nguurndam e cowale [lepte] kumayde refti he…ďantaake ma ballo e hoore Amen."
  17,76,"Fii kala …ďe e…ď…ďiino dillinngol ma ka leydi fii yo …ďe yaltine e mayri, on tuma …ďe √Īii…ďataano …ďatte maa si wonaa see…óa."
  17,77,"∆äum ko Sunna …ďe …ďe min n nuli ko adimaa immorde e Nulaa…ďe amen, a he…ďantaa Sunna amen on mbattiigu."
  17,78,"√Ďii…ďu juulde nde ka mortagol na'ange nge haa ka ni…ďre jemma, Juulde subaha nde, pellet, Juulde subaha nde wonii seedeteende."
  17,79,"Ka jemma tinno e makko ko …ďeydaari maa…óa, no jortaa nde Joomi maa…óa immintinat ma e daror…óe yettiniinde."
  17,80,"Ma'aku: ""Jooma, naadira naatirgal goonga yaltiniraa mi jaltirgal goonga, mba…óanaa mi immorde ka maa…óa doole ballal""."
  17,81,"Maaku: ""goonga o arii mehre nde fuuyii, pellet, mehre nde wonii fuuyoore""."
  17,82,"Mi…óen tellina ka Alqur'aana hu'unde nde konde cellal e yurmeende wona'nde gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe, …ďeydataa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen si wonaa hayre."
  17,83,"Si min n nee…ďnii e ne…ó…óaŇčke on o …óuurnoo o townaa balaaje makko, si bone he…ďii mo o wona hattu…óo e ta∆īii…óo."
  17,84,"Maaku: ""mo kala yo gollu…óo e laawol mum, ko Joomi mon woni ganndu…óo on …ďur…óo feewde laawol""."
  17,85,"He…ďe la…ďdo maa fii fittaandu, maaku: ""Fittaandu ndu ko e fiyaake Joomi an, on okkaaka e ganndal si wonaa see…óa√©."
  17,86,"Mi woondii, si Mi…óen nji…ónoo min na…ďatno nde hu'unde nde min wahyini fa'ade e maa…óa, refti he…ďantaake ma fawtii…óo …óum e hoore amen."
  17,87,"Ko woni tan, ko Hinnayee immorde ka Joomi maa, pellet, …ďural makko ngal e dow maa wonii mawngal."
  17,88,"Maaku: ""Mi woondii, si yim…ďe …ďe e jinnaaji …ói kawtitii fii yo …ďe ngaddu yeru ndee Alqur'aanaare, …ďe mgaddataa yeru mayre, hay si wonii wo…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe ko wallindrat…ďe e wo…ď…ďe""."
  17,89,"GooŇč…óii min …ďannginanii yim…ďe …ďen e ndee Alqur'aanaare immorde e kala misal, …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďe calii, si wanaa jeddugol."
  17,90,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""min ngoŇč…óintaa ma, haa …ďullitanaa men e lesdi …ďunndu""."
  17,91,"Mu …óum laatano maa ngesa immorde e tamorooje e inabuuje …ďullitaa caatli …ói hakkunde majje …ďullitugol."
  17,92,"Ma …óum li…ďaa kammu ngu e hoore amen wano aa∆īor…óaa non kunte, maa …óum ngddaa Alla e Maleykaaji …ói [men] kuccandira."
  17,93,"Ma …óum laatano maa suudu immorde e cu…óaaje [kanŇče], maa…óum ∆īawaa ka kammu, men ngooŇč…óintaa ∆īawugol maa…óa ngol haa njippinaa e amen deftere men jannga nde. Maaku: ""Senaade Jom an, hara mi wonu, ko wonaa …ďanndinke Nulaa…óo?!""."
  17,94,"Ha…óaani yim…ďe …ďe nde …ďe ngooŇč…óinta tuma nde peewalngal arnoo …ďe, si wonaa fii …ďe mbi'i i'ii: ""E hara Alla nulay …ďanndiŇčke Nulaa…óo?!"""
  17,95,"Maaku: ""Si tawiino laatinooma lesdi maleykaaji he…ďe njaha ko …ďe dee∆ī…ďe, min njippinatno e ma…ď…ďe immorde ka kammu Malayla Nulaa…óo""."
  17,96,"Maaku: ""Alla yonii ceedii…óo hakkunde am e mon, pellet KaŇčko o wonii kumpitii…óo deen…óo jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen""."
  17,97,"Oon mo Alla feewni ko oon woni peewu…óo, …ďe o majjini …ďe a he…ďantaa…ďe walloo…ďe ko woori mo. Min moo…ďay …ďe √Īande darnga e dow je'ece ma…ď…ďe …óe ko …ďe wum…ďe e muum…óu…ďe= fahdube …ďe e faa…óu…ďe, ja'a∆īndee ma…ď…ďe nden ko jahannama tuma kala nge rocci min …ďeydana …ďe hu…ď…ďunge."
  17,98,"∆äuum ko njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe, sabu kam…ďe …ďe njeddii aayeeje amen …óe, …ďe mbi'i i: ""E hay si min ngonii ∆īi'e e mbu…óu e hara minen ko min immintintee…ďe tagoore?!"" hesre."
  17,99,"Enee, …ďee nji'aani, won'de Alla O Tak…óo kammuuli …ói e leydi ndi ko kattan…óo nde o tagata yeru ma…ď…ďe, o wa…óani …ďe lajal [caate] sikke alaa e maggal. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďe calii si wonaa jeddugol."
  17,100,"Maaku: ""Sinndo onon ho…óon marnoo ngaluuji yurmeende e Joomi am on, on tuma, on njogitotono kulol nafkugol, ne…ó…óaŇčke on wonii nguddo""."
  17,101,"GooŇč…óii min n ngkkiino Muusaa aayeeje jeenay …ďanngu…óe, lanndii …ďi…ď…ďe Israa'iila …ďen tuma nde o arnoo …ďe Fir'awna wi'ani mo: ""min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbil…óaa…óo""."
  17,102,"Maaku: ""GooŇč…óii ha…óa anndi jippinaani …óee si wonaa Jey…óo kammuuji …ói e leydi ndi aayeeje [yi'etee…ói]. Min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a kalkii…óo""."
  17,103,"O faalaa nde o dillinta …ďe ka lesdi min n njoooli mo e …ďe won'du …ďe e makko …ďe denndaangal."
  17,104,"Min Daalani …ďaawo makko …ďi…ď…ďe Israa'iila …ďe: ""Ho…óee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, min ngaddana on ko on muu…ďii…ďe=fiiliibe""."
  17,105,"Ko sabu Goonga min telliniri nde, ko sabu Goonga nde tellii, Min nuliraani ma si wanaa [ko a] beltinoowo=beltinoowo e jertinoowo."
  17,106,"E Qur'aanaare min n …ďanngini nde fii yo a janngannde yim…ďe …ďe e dow dee∆īere, min njippini nde jippin'de."
  17,107,"Maaku: ""ngooŇč…óinee nde, maa…óum wota on ngoŇč…óine, pellet, …ďen okkaa…ďe ganndal ko adii nde si [nde] janngaama e taweende ma…ď…ďe …ďe suuyiray wokku…óe ko …ďe sujjoo…ďe""."
  17,108,"∆Āe mbi'a:Senaade woodanii Joomi amen,nde wonnoo Fodoore Joomi amen nden ko wa…óoore."
  17,109,"He…ďe suuyira wokku…óe …ďe ngulla [Alqur'aana on] …ďasda …ďe yankinaare."
  17,110,"Maaku: ""Noddiree mo Alla maa noddiro mo jurmotoo…óo, kala no noddir…óon Mo, ko KaŇčko In…óe Mo∆ī∆īe …óen heeranii, wota a fen√Īin juulde maa…óa nden wota a suu…ónde nde …óa…ď…ďu hakkunde …óuum laawol."
  17,111,"Maaku: jettooje …óe ngoodanii Alla o mo jogitaaki …ďi…ó…óo laatanaaki mo kafidaa…óo e Laamu laatanaaki mo teddu…óo mo o huykinantoo, Mawnin Mo Mawnin'dee."
